name: ZOrderMethod
shortdesc: How to re-arrange the art item.

property.name: BRINGTOFRONT
property.shortdesc: Move art to front of it's group or layer.

property.name: BRINGFORWARD
property.shortdesc: Move art one step forward in it's group or layer.

property.name: SENDBACKWARD
property.shortdesc: Move art one step backwards in it's group or layer.

property.name: SENDTOBACK
property.shortdesc: Move art to back of it's group or layer.
